 HEFEI, NOV. 19 (Xinhua) -- At a time when the global economy is facing unprecedented challenges, Chinese manufacturing has provided reliable support for stabilizing the global industrial chain and supply chain. From the rooftop photovoltaic power station in Indonesia to the production workshop in east China's Anhui, take a journey with Xinhua correspondents on the cooperation between Chinese manufacturing and global industry.  Aerial photo taken on Nov. 18, 2021 shows workshops producing photovoltaic power equipment in Hefei, east China's Anhui Province. (Xinhua/Huang Bohan)  Aerial photo taken on Nov. 18, 2021 shows the rooftop photovoltaic power station at a site of a photovoltaic power equipment workshop in Hefei, east China's Anhui Province. (Xinhua/Huang Bohan)  Workers work at a photovoltaic power equipment workshop in Hefei, east China's Anhui Province, Nov. 18, 2021. (Xinhua/Huang Bohan)  A worker works at a photovoltaic power equipment workshop in Hefei, east China's Anhui Province, Nov. 18, 2021. (Xinhua/Huang Bohan)  Photo taken on Nov. 18, 2021 shows a rooftop photovoltaic power station in East Java, Indonesia. (Xinhua/Wang Aona)  Photo taken on Nov. 18, 2021 shows a rooftop photovoltaic power station in East Java, Indonesia. (Xinhua/Wang Aona)â–  